                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/2649: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Warren</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-08-28T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>95. Your No. 135, August 9, 1 p.m. and No. 140, August 23, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>Suggestion of Japanese Government is today being brought to attention of British,
                    French and Italian Governments.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
